edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.util

Class LinkedListRecursive<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.util.LinkedListRecursive<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - Generic type

    public class LinkedListRecursive<E>
extends java.lang.Object
    Class defines state and behavior for a recursive LinkedList. Inner ListNode class defines state of list elements and recursive behavior of outer methods. Functionality is provided for add, remove, get, set, and various data boolean checks. To be used with FacultySchedule.
    Author:
    Nick Garner
